Package: dejuNeonRootSoil
Type: Package
Title: NEON Root Chemistry and Soil Bulk Density Analysis Framework
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Sergio", "Ocampo", email = "socampo3@dons.usfca.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive framework for analyzing root chemistry and soil bulk density relationships 
    across NEON sites. Provides tools for data acquisition, processing, statistical modeling, and 
    visualization of belowground carbon and nitrogen dynamics. Designed for ecological researchers 
    studying root-soil interactions in terrestrial ecosystems.
